
NOTE:  You must have the blas library installed somewhere on your
system.  Set the variable BLASLOC in the makefile to the location of your
BLAS.  (Or type make BLASLOC=<location of blas>).  Someday I will learn how
to use autoconfig, etc.  Be patient with my crude compile scripts.

Some simple installation instructions:

Modify the following files to reflect your installation:

Makefile
SuperLU/make.inc
sparsekit/Makefile

Type:
make libs    to make the needed libraries (not the BLAS though)
make         to make the extensions modules

Place the extension modules somewhere in your Python path:

